thread.title: Otto

author: Otto
title: Otto
text:
We thought James and Kristian did a really good job selling our property and we're happy with the result.
James performed superbly during the auction and did really well to extract all the potential out of our property.
During the campaign there was plenty of feedback on how things were going, who was seriously interested and the process felt collaborative.
Perfect choice of agent for our inner north property.
